# GitHub Workflow

- **Repository:** `morphingcoffee/GameLauncher` (public)
- **Prefer GitHub MCP** for issues, PRs, project board, and Actions status before shell fallbacks
- **Link work to issues:** branch names like `phase-N/short-desc`; PR body includes `Closes #N`
- **Project board:** repository-level "Game Launcher Roadmap" (record project number here after creation)
- **Before commit/push:** follow `secret-hygiene` skill; run `tools/dev/scan-secrets.sh`
- **Secrets:** PAT only in macOS Keychain (`security`); inject via `tools/dev/github-pat-from-keychain.sh` or `tools/dev/open-cursor-with-github.sh` — never in project config files; global MCP config at `~/.cursor/mcp.json` uses `${env:GITHUB_PAT}` only
